parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Rear Brake Lockup in Damp or Wet Conditions
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The rear brakes locking up in damp or wet conditions can cause loss of control, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: Rear brakes lock up when applying pressure to the brake pedal
especially in damp or wet road conditions
causing the vehicle to pull to one side or lose traction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ABS system can cause loss of control, accidents, and injuries, especially in wet or slippery road conditions.
symptoms: ABS warning light comes on
brake pedal feels hard or unresponsive
vehicle pulls to one side or loses traction
rear brakes lock up
or the vehicle experiences shimmying when applying brakes.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Brake fluid leaks can cause loss of braking power, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: Brake fluid is leaking
causing the rear brakes not to work
or the brake pedal feels soft or spongy.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Warped front brake rotors can cause vibrations, noise, and reduced braking performance, increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: Vibrations or noise when applying brakes
warped front brake rotors require frequent replacement.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Wheel cylinder failure can cause loss of braking power, accidents, and injuries.
symptoms: Wheel cylinder freezes
causing the brakes to lock up or fail to function properly.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Unrelated electrical issues can cause distractions, loss of control, and accidents.
symptoms: Windshield washers and wipers come on unexpectedly
impairing the driver's vision.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The intermittent failure of the windshield wipers can cause poor visibility, especially during rain or snow, which can lead to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: Windshield wipers come on without command
windshield wipers quit working in the middle of operation
windshield wipers continue to operate after being turned off
windshield wipers activate on their own and cut off
windshield washer sprays solution on occasions when wipers activate
loss of vision due to wiper malfunction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the control unit can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to a loss of control and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or loses power
especially when driving at high speeds (over 60 mph).

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The vehicle stalling can cause a loss of control, increasing the risk of accidents, and potentially leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls while driving at any speed.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The ignition switch short can cause the vehicle to stall or fail to start, leading to a loss of control and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The ignition switch fails to function properly
causing the vehicle to stall or fail to start.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag to deploy in a collision can lead to serious injuries or fatalities, as the occupant is not provided with the necessary protection to absorb the impact.
symptoms: Airbag does not deploy in a collision
resulting in injuries or fatalities.
